Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Close proximity to all local amenity

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Western Sydney are excited to present to the market 21 Deakin Street, West Ryde.

This is an excellent opportunity for developers and investors looking for an effortless build. Situated in the thriving West Ryde corridor, this townhouse development site is zoned R2 and moments from all public amenities.

- DA Approved for 3 townhouses
- Existing building: 6 bedrooms/4 bathrooms/6 car spots 
- R2 - Low Density Residential 
- Land Area of 999.4sqm*
- Flat, regular shaped site 
- Close-proximity to all local amenity 
- Outstanding accessibility to public transport 
- 1.5km* to West Ryde Station & Meadowbank Station.  
- Development: Construction of a new multi-dwelling housing development comprising of 3 dwellings - 1 x two storey 5-bedroom dwelling, a 2 x single storey 3-bedroom units as well as strata subdivision

For further information please contact the listed, exclusive agents.

*approx
